  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat (400°F/200°C).",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together grill seasoning, olive oil, garlic, onion, bell pepper, tomato, cumin, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken drumsticks to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Thread the marinated chicken onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "Grill the kebabs for 8-10 minutes per side, or until the chicken is cooked through and the vegetables are tender.",
    "Let the kebabs rest for 5 minutes before serving.",
